        "id": 2039968,
        "name": "J\u00fcrgen Schmidt",
        "username": "Martin_Zwick",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/9fc29f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-10-26T11:02:44.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>2016 Keller</p>\n<p>\u201cWe have still 10 days ahead - 2016 goes in the direction of 2002. Cool, not too much alcohol, very pure, racy and quality. Botrytis very rare - a vintage for Kabinett and the dry ones. Like we love it.\u201d KP Keller</p>\n<p><em>\u201cWir haben noch 10 Tage vor uns \u2013 2016 geht in Richtung 2002. K\u00fchl, nicht zu viel Alk, sehr pur, Rasse und Klasse. Botrytis ganz rar \u2013 ein Jahr f\u00fcr Kabinette und die trockenen. Genauso, wie wir es uns w\u00fcnschen.\u201d</em> KP Keller<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/a/3/a398d7c0ad7246144f25e3a6b99840859ef740f9.jpeg\" alt=\"Morstein.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"nlfi5OYkficdDjao6fWg70B4gQN\" width=\"270\" height=\"480\"><br>\nMORSTEIN<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nGin Gin<br>\nMartin<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nP.S.  and the usual comments about <em>Propaganda</em> or hype, please keep it.  Of course the truth lies in the glass.</p>",
